hopobject.body: How much notice do you have to give? smart bandages article Looking forward, the firm now sees fiscal 2013 revenue in the range of $1.625 billion - $1.635 billion and earnings per share to be in the $1.94 - $1.97 range. Analysts anticipate full-year earnings of $1.99 per share and revenue of $1.67 billion. Earlier, lululemon projected net revenue in the range of $1.645 billion - $1.665 billion and earnings of $1.96 - $2.01 per share for the full year.
